hods developed in this work will be used to study Mg abundances of a\nlarge sample of stars in the next paper in the series.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 21 Dec 2016 21:52:10 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 13 Jul 2017 14:05:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-09-27"}
