om graph, and the random poset.\n  Finally, we provide a new and short proof, in the language of monoids, of the\ntheorem stating that every $\\omega$-categorical structure is homomorphically\nequivalent to a model-complete core.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 22 Dec 2016 11:36:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 9 Jan 2017 21:06:50 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 23 Sep 2018 15:19:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-09-25"}
